Reasoning: The paper deals with personalization in online services, specifically search engines, news websites, and ad providers. This falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses privacy concerns, which could fall under the category of Cybersecurity (cs.CR) or Cyberlaw (cs.CY). The use of machine learning algorithms to capture personalization vectors and build a privacy evaluation framework could also fall under the category of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
